+{"id":"frankenpandas-ouqtz","title":"fd90.132: ExprError row says UnknownColumn but actual variant is UnknownSeries (phantom variant)","description":"fd90.74-131 README audit. Error Architecture table at line 827 shows:
  | ExprError | fp-expr | ParseError(String), UnknownColumn(String), UnknownLocal(String) |

Verified against crates/fp-expr/src/lib.rs:219:
  pub enum ExprError {
      UnknownSeries(String),    // <-- README says UnknownColumn (wrong!)
      UnknownLocal(String),
      UnanchoredLiteral,
      UnanchoredLocal(String),
      ParseError(String),
      Frame(FrameError),
  }

The variant 'UnknownColumn' DOES NOT EXIST. The actual variant is 'UnknownSeries' (the parser's column-name lookups fail through the Series-resolution path).

A user pattern-matching with Err(ExprError::UnknownColumn(name)) hits:
  error[E0599]: no variant or associated item named 'UnknownColumn' found

Fix: UnknownColumn → UnknownSeries. Pure README change.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"bug","created_at":"2026-04-26T12:22:33.367377061Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-26T12:23:42.251253999Z","closed_at":"2026-04-26T12:23:42.248545852Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
